{
  "text": "Customer expectation (CE) also plays an important role in a customer's assessment of foods [CITATION_1] . Research has shown that different levels of expectation have an influence on assessing the quality level of food products (cf. [CITATION_2] . At the same time, 'expectation is based on the customer's needs and wishes' [CITATION_3] . An important part of customer expectations also takes the form of the establishment and filfillment of promises, although the literature looks more at services in this regard (cf. [CITATION_4] .",
